{"tid":376334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【帕卡襲澳】下午1時前或改發三號風球","createTime":"2017-08-27T02:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T02:45:15.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52837bfae3a4017d5a6dc408f45cdceefd9b3144","tid":376334,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T02:24:59.000Z","msg":"強烈熱帶風暴「帕卡」吹襲下，本港及澳門都懸掛了八號風球。其中澳門氣象局表示，「帕卡」已於台山市登陸，預測澳門風力將會減弱，下午1時前考慮改發三號風球；本港天文台則指，過去一小時，香港西南部仍然間中吹暴風，而大嶼山高地間中達颶風程度，預計八號烈風或暴風信號會在上午維持。<br />\n<br />\n上午10時，「帕卡」集結在香港天文台以西約120公里，預料向西北偏北移動，時速約28公里，移入廣東內陸。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170827/s00001/1503800055130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170827%2Fs00001%2F1503800055130&d=qwbY4yp6nOJo4LhtWdkQJdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=92d6cf0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170827%2Fs00001%2F1503800055130&h=882fcd3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170827/s00001/1503800055130</a>"},{"pid":"ec33fd1d07822573e56e39de505331be6cdc05cd","tid":376334,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T02:29:17.000Z","msg":"上次時速60，今次28<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廢左d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83cb90c3c103bf8d5397e6eb7ed7162d8f481e16","tid":376334,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T02:29:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次時速60，今次28<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廢左d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咦唔係，睇錯當我無講過"},{"pid":"e01805ce2581010fe9775c537910dcf2b8886e9a","tid":376334,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T02:30:28.000Z","msg"